{"tid":1722441,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實你地係咪唔知政府打梗民意戰？","createTime":"2019-11-15T01:44:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T01:53:40.000Z","uid":263064,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"36ba10d389807a9c35ef4841e1a349489d3fdf18","tid":1722441,"uid":263064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T01:44:06.000Z","msg":"你地睇下，琴晚燒到咁，消防員出來既次數仲多過啲狗出來。燒完，消防員救火，啲狗掟幾粒催淚彈就走。然後成件事再不斷重複。<br />\n<br />\n跟住有時係街道放tg 既話，啲狗就係咁開咪講：<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">「請你地唔好再掟磚啦，我地施放催淚彈架啦！</span></strong>」等等，不斷將自己擺係被動既位，拉民意。<br />\n<br />\n大三罷之後佢地既部署一日靜過一日，好大機會就係佢地想等民意誅殺我地。大家記住梁天崎果句：「革命係要令唔支持我地既人支持我地先會成功。」，依家呢個樽頸位，我地真係要<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好好諗下應該點做</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n大家係度留言講講有咩方法交流下，我都諗左好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<em><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">另外想同某啲話人五毛分化撚講，每個人有自己唔同意見，說好的不割蓆不分化呢？人地一講啲唔岩聽就話係五毛，同啲藍絲冇分別架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></em>"},{"pid":"604b29dcd0e3bc2e94c5f617635deb6d84b568af","tid":1722441,"uid":262035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T01:51:44.000Z","msg":"仲講民意戰？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n坐左幾耐呀？"},{"pid":"a103bd6e70c22148ece2942bc6908e66c4de4b64","tid":1722441,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T01:53:40.000Z","msg":"拉"}]}